title: LOL rap by Rockit Gaming

embed.description: iTunes: https://itun.es/us/4OUObb Google Play:https://play.google.com/store/music/album/Rockit_Gaming_In_the_League_feat_Dr_G?id=Bdmx3vwqmceivrg6qbqvr3jdsni The wait is finally here. body:
Hello Fellow gamers and things I don't need to say

I found a Rap on League of legends by Rockit Gaming that I think is pretty cool on Youtube,
would love to hear your thoughts.

P.S {{champion:222}}  is the best... I think.
TheWindy42

replies.body:
Video is actually.... pretty good.

- It's from April though, so it's not new or anything.

- Rockit gaming is a publishing channel for gaming songs, so there's a lot of other cool content there, just not LoL related.

- 20 god damn seconds to get to the start of a video......... so many people have left by that stage.
I know that's the only thing you have to wait for but the song is good Quality
All I'm hearing is auto-tuned crap?
Sorry, I got to 1:31 and had to stop. That's not rap, that's auto-tuned to hell crap.
none taken, it's just an opinion. :)
